Subject: [PATCH 2/6] GH-33882: [C++] Don't find .pc files with
 ARROW_BUILD_STATIC=OFF (#34019)

Because they are needless and `pkg-config grpc++` is slow.

Don't find .pc files with `ARROW_BUILD_STATIC=OFF`.

Yes.

No.
* Closes: #33882

